  abstract = {In this pedagogical proposal, a problem question is presented that associates the use of artificial intelligence in the learning of trigonometric functions, with the objective of strengthening the pedagogical and cognitive bases in the learning of trigonometry in tenth grade students of the Institution. . Educational San Juan Bautista de la Salle. When carrying out the proposal, it was evident that students have many shortcomings in the mathematical tools of previous years, which causes them to have difficulties when solving problem situations related to trigonometry, which has generated low performance in tenth grade students. Students have not had the pedagogical tools capable of generating critical thinking in them that allows them to analyze a situation related to trigonometry. Then, based on this, a didactic sequence is applied based on the use of artificial intelligence and the Khan Academic digital tool, with the aim of generating motivation in students and strengthening the ability of students to solve exercises related to trigonometry.},
